&lt;p&gt;At DICE, you’ll be part of the company that’s redefining live entertainment. It&#39;s a place where you can be yourself, influence the culture, and create work that you’re proud of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for an experienced commercial leader to join the team at DICE. You’ll be accountable for driving exponential growth amongst North America’s leading venues and promoters in the USA, Canada, and future expansion into Mexico. You will work closely with internal stakeholders in wider global markets to ensure all business opportunities are maximised, with a focus on regional expansion and new partnerships.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We know the power of live will never go away; you will be joining at a time when DICE’s legacy in the live space is coming into full force, helping our much-loved partners innovate and grow.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
