&lt;p&gt;The Senior Sales Lead&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;will report to the Director of Sales, North America, and work as part of the Sales Leadership Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll be&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
