&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Educating your network about DICE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resetting the DICE brand in the market, working with the teams on creative ways to get DICE and the teams front and centre in each market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thinking outside of the box to remain competitive and ahead of our competitors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using our strategy to find new business for the team across lead generation, deal modelling, negotiation and closing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Driving the strategy for expansion into new cities within existing markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with the Sales Operations team to fine-tune processes, systems and reports to monitor growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with Operations to make sure deals go smoothly.Working closely with Operations and Product to ensure seamless partner onboarding and execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate, humble and talented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A fan of music and culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Actively responsible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comfortable under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
